data.description: This exceptional golf course home is nestled on nearly three secluded acres behind the private gates of the prestigious Overlook at River Crossing. River crossing is minutes away from Highway 281 and Highway 46. Entertain your guests and family in the backyard with outdoor kitchen, fire pit, large bar and an expansive deck. The pool features a hot tub and infinity edge pool with a cascading waterfall into a lower wading pool. Practice your golf skills on your own private putting and chipping green. The impressive living room features floor to ceiling windows,  Austin-cut limestone and natural wood accents. The high end kitchen is a chef's dream with a Viking stove, Bosch microwave and Subzero Refrigerator. Each of the four bedrooms offers a walk-in closet and en suite bath. The home office also features an en suite bath. This beautiful home includes a media room with six built in leather movie chairs. Two separate large garages accommodate five vehicles. One of the garages is temperature controlled which makes it a perfect work space if desired. The back yard has a third garage to store your golf cart. This house has it all!
